'''''Planet of the Apps''''' is an American [[Reality television#Documentary-style|reality television show]] broadcast on [[Apple Music]]. It is the first original television show produced by [[Apple Inc.|Apple]]. On July 23, 2018, it was announced that Apple had canceled the series after one season.<ref>{{cite web |last1=Clover |first1=Juli |title='Planet of the Apps' Star Gary Vaynerchuk Blames Show's Failure on Apple's Poor Marketing |url=https://www.macrumors.com/2018/07/23/planet-of-the-apps-gary-vaynerchuk/ |website=[[MacRumors]] |accessdate=July 24, 2018 |language=en |date=July 23, 2018}}</ref>

==Episode style==
On each of the episode, [[software]] makers have 60 seconds to pitch their idea in front of the judges ([[Jessica Alba]], [[Gwyneth Paltrow]], [[will.i.am]] and [[Gary Vaynerchuk]]) on a slow-moving [[escalator]]—for a visual idea of an "[[elevator pitch]]". New episodes were released on Tuesdays, with the first season being 10 episodes long.<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-apple-television-apps-idUSKBN18X32P |title=Apple's first TV series shows what it takes to build an app |date=2017-06-09 |agency=Reuters|access-date=2017-06-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170614132324/http://www.reuters.com/article/us-apple-television-apps-idUSKBN18X32P |archivedate=2017-06-14 |df=}}</ref> The series is hosted by [[Zane Lowe]] and produced by [[Ben Silverman]].<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/reviews/planet-of-the-apps-apple-gwyneth-paltrow-jessica-alba-1202456477/ |title=TV Review: Apple’s ‘Planet of the Apps’ |last=Ryan |first=Maureen |date=2017-06-07 |work=Variety|access-date=2017-06-15  |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619204025/http://variety.com/2017/tv/reviews/planet-of-the-apps-apple-gwyneth-paltrow-jessica-alba-1202456477/ |archivedate=2017-06-19 |df=}}</ref> The series premiered on June 6, 2017.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/06/06/apple-music-planet-of-the-apps-premiere/ |title=Apple Music's 'Planet of the Apps' reality show debuts tonight |website=Engadget|access-date=2017-06-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613022419/https://www.engadget.com/2017/06/06/apple-music-planet-of-the-apps-premiere/ |archivedate=2017-06-13 |df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://techcrunch.com/2017/06/07/apples-debut-tv-series-planet-of-the-apps-kicks-off/ |title=Apple’s debut TV series, Planet of the Apps, kicks off |last=Lomas |first=Natasha |publisher=TechCrunch|access-date=2017-06-14 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170613105648/https://techcrunch.com/2017/06/07/apples-debut-tv-series-planet-of-the-apps-kicks-off/ |archivedate=2017-06-13 |df=}}</ref>

